>\n<br />\n如果你想進一步確定，就係你可以輕撫佢背脊先，慢慢咁咁擺隻手指摸佢大肚兩邊，睇下會唔會有少少硬物郁，因為咁大個肚應該已經會胎動，bb 會腳仔踢媽媽個肚。當然你唔可以驚動到媽媽，媽媽會驚有人搞佢肚。<br />\n<br />\n另外要留意返媽媽幾大，因為天竺鼠太細會容易難產，但係太過大，佢地個盆骨會收細，咁都好大機會難產，咁到時媽媽都會死，所以如果天竺鼠媽媽如果已經8-9個月大，就唔建議生，要開刀做手術"},{"pid":"6b967afde4e0c56f1dc41fdcc7fc7452289a7075","tid":1904562,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"大力㩒下佢個肚"},{"pid":"00f82953082a472f63ed607a8e1274150c756cfb","tid":1904562,"uid":6747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1318389497200344a41455e79b27ad7c31d7d6be","tid":1904562,"uid":261290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:59:13.000Z","msg":"我買左佢一個月，買既時候佢係一個人訓無同其他鼠合籠，岩岩買回來係咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/01/005531_0a1f711faa44b1d3188154873d3c47e4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F01%2F005531_0a1f711faa44b1d3188154873d3c47e4.jpeg&h=91537193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢一直都食好多野架食唔停咁<br />\n<br />\n到近排唔知佢肥左定係寵物店一早比鼠搞大左，佢又無唔比我抱，脾氣都無變又唔惡，但只係個肚肥上半身又唔肥咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家一個月後係變成咁架<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOyLv2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOyLv2k.jpg&h=2aa0e6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我上網睇左好多資料話有左會成日都叫，佢又唔會叫架平時，我打左幾間獸醫都唔睇天竺鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無養過養緊既可以答下我，求下你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse